-- BHP Billiton, Abramovich May Tap Russian Gold, Kommersant Says
-- B y   S t e p h e n   B i e r m a n
-- 2012-06-28T04:28:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/bhp-billiton-abramovich-may-tap-russian-gold-kommersant-says.html
Russian billionaire  Roman Abramovich ’s Millhouse group is in talks with  BHP Billiton Ltd. (BHP) 
on a partnership to mine for gold and copper in Russia’s Far
East,  Kommersant  reported, citing an unidentified person
familiar with the matter.  The two companies may agree on a venture by the end of the
year to develop the Baimsk block in Russia’s Chukotka region,
the newspaper said, adding that Melbourne-based BHP Billiton may
take 75 percent and Millhouse the rest.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Bierman in Moscow at 
